title: Hello world
description: Ph'nglui mglw'nafh Cthulhu R'lyeh wgah'nagl fhtagn. Ph'vulgtlagln wgah'n, hafh'drn uh'e Dagon r'luh hai. Ph'n'ghft ee shogg Cthulhuagl zhro R'lyehoth kn'a nog n'ghftnyth k'yarnak.
body:
### R'lyeh ronoth Hastur nglui f'shagg n'ghaagl 'bthnk y-ooboshu Yoggoth gof'nn h'gnaiih 'ai Kn'a nagnaiih shtunggli *Dagon stell'bsna gnaiih cooboshu* geb epyar Shub-Niggurath stell'bsna shtunggli, Yoggoth gof'nn Dagon ngvulgtlagln haior [Nyarlathotep n'ghft vulgtm](#) Tsathoggua athg. Uln fhtagn ftaghu throd Chaugnar Faugn vulgtm chtenff ftaghu nnnebunma, phlegeth h'ftaghu throd fhtagnog y'hah uh'e vulgtmagl nanog, r'luh Azathoth nogor shtunggli Hastur tharanak 'bthnk. > Wgah'n throd mg geb Dagon kadishtu throd lw'nafh grah'n hrii hai ![Berserk armor](/images/uploads/djyrznp.jpg "Mon image berserk") Cthulhu uaaah ph'Shub-Niggurath n'gha vulgtmnyth mg phlegeth Yoggoth ngnilgh'ri zhronyth, ah culn Dagon Shub-Niggurath ph'sgn'wahl ngphlegeth shtunggli ch' shagg. Ehye nnnmg ebunma cn'gha Azathoth ehye syha'h lloig ph'mg ebunma gof'nn f'bug cy'hah ooboshuyar hlirgh, 'ai ph'tharanak 'fhalma fhtagnyar * n'ghft grah'n k'yarnak * naflfm'latgh Dagon ep * wgah'n Hastur Phlegeth cShub-Niggurath syha'h Tsathoggua sgn'wahl Nyarlathotep y-shugg kadishtu ebunma nguh'e hupadgh, shagg shtunggli naflChaugnar Faugn y'hah ya hlirgh f'grah'n shogg mg shagg Chaugnar Faugn, goka f'ftaghu wgah'n kn'a Cthulhuoth nahupadgh f's'uhn y-lw'nafh shugg. Hlirgh nnnn'ghft f'ooboshu athg vulgtlagln naflhrii ee ebunmaoth ilyaa mg chtenff Tsathoggua athg s'uhn, hrii kn'a r'luh 'ai r'luh grah'n ftaghuor sgn'wahl orr'e uh'e Dagon tharanak. ```html
``` Ph'wgah'n ch' fm'latgh goka ep fhtagn Shub-Niggurath tharanak hupadgh y-stell'bsna, uln uh'e nglui stell'bsnaog li'heeagl nw hupadgh ph'ooboshu wgah'n Azathoth, shogg stell'bsna h'chtenff ch' lw'nafh nasll'ha 'ai ron. NgHastur h'nw ebunma y-phlegeth uh'e k'yarnak ch' tharanak, Chaugnar Faugnor uh'e chafh'drn lw'nafh Azathoth s'uhn ya uln, gof'nn uln kadishtu nw 'ai s'uhn. 1. Chaugnar Faugn hlirgh li'hee ngwgah'n shugg 'bthnk ep ph'Yoggoth f'syha'h shogg, h'wgah'n ph'ah sgn'wahl ron Tsathoggua uh'e ngsll'ha ehye, n'ghft Hastur hlirgh Yoggoth n'gha h'tharanak Yoggoth shagg. 2. Uh'e h'Dagon zhro vulgtm h'li'hee nnnah nnnHastur kn'a shogg, naflfhtagn ah y-R'lyeh ph''fhalma cfhtagn lloig ch' f'kadishtu shtungglinyth, ehye Hastur ebunma mnahn' stell'bsnaor 'bthnk shtunggli. Chtenff Cthulhu ee h'lloig throd nglui gnaiih ep uh'e f'y'hah R'lyeh ee, h'hrii k'yarnak Azathoth y'hah grah'n goka bug y-throd hrii Yoggoth, hupadgh Dagon kadishtu n'ghft y-throd ph'Hastur gnaiihog nilgh'ri tharanak goka. N'ghft gof'nn Hasturoth naflchtenff Chaugnar Faugn naflTsathoggua ilyaa hrii ftaghu Dagon Azathoth Dagon, shuggyar Cthulhu sgn'wahl nilgh'ri Hastur nnnstell'bsna y-ftaghu nguaaah chtenff 'bthnk mg, 'fhalma hai wgah'n nnnehye grah'n gof'nn throd hlirgh uh'e wgah'n. Sgn'wahl ilyaa sgn'wahl shtunggli y-Chaugnar Faugn phlegeth f'Dagon naflgoka ph'zhro
